This directory contains software tools for lab 2 in COMP 506.

  -- lab2_ref is a reference implementation of the lab
     You may execute it on the CLEAR systems.  The -v flag 
     increases the level of comments in the generated ILOC 
     code.

  -- sim is the ILOC simulator for this lab. Its documentation
     is found on the course web site and in the file SimDoc.pdf
     in this directory.  

     The tar archive file contains the source code for the simulator.
     You may wish to build a copy on your own machine to simplify 
     debugging.

